+{error_block}
+Baseline summary for orientation only: {baseline_results}
+{problem_context}
+After writing the exact JSON, stop. Do not answer ALL_COMPLETED until run_1 through run_4 have all executed."""
+
+
+def _write_exact_policy(folder_name, idea, run_num):
